|YKODarkWind has a simple, but intricate ferry system. There are currently four
ferries that will sail you around the lands of DarkWind. Near the docks you
will find someone selling tickets. Tickets are free to those level 5 and
under, and 85 coins for everyone else.

* The M.S.S Fairweather sails from DarkWind to Souvrael and back.
* The whaling ship Pequod sails from Hyperborea to DarkWind and back.
* The Oshimara Maru sails from Souvrael to the Odako province of Kerei and back.
* The Island Skipper sails from DarkWind to the Isle of Dwork, then to Volcano
  Isle, then back to DarkWind.
